Build Requirements:
GCC 4.6 or later
Linux kernel version 4.13.0-45-generic 
/*The codeworks perfectly on kernel version 4.13, issues have been found while implementing it on version 4.15*/

Compilation/Installation:
run the script run.sh
/*run.sh executes all the functions which builds the ovs code, installs it creates a kernel module and loads it on the kernel*/

